<h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Patch 37 (October 21, 2014)</h4><ul><li><b>Flourish (W)</b></li><ul><li> Updated the tool-tip on this ability to reflect the fact that it cannot be used to dash over terrain.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Patch 36 (September 30, 2014)</h4><ul><li><b>Captivate (Q)</b></li><ul><li> This ability will now always cast to maximum range.</li></ul><li><b>Flourish (W)</b></li><ul><li> Fixed a bug where King of Masks could lose the empowered component of his Captivate (Q) or Endless Delights (E) if he was silenced during their casts immediately after using Flourish (W).</li><li> This ability may now be cast during a Captivate (Q) or Endless Delights (E) cast animation without cancelling the abilities.</li><li> Casting Captivate (Q) or Endless Delights (E) during a Flourish (W) will now instantly cast them from King of Masks' position, rather than after a delay.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 34 (August 19th, 2014)</h4><ul><li><b>Captivate (Q)</b></li><ul><li>The damage dealt per tentacle hit has been reduced to 25/45/65/85/105, down from 35/55/75/95/115.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 31 (June 17th, 2014)</h4><ul><li><B>Captivate (Q)</B></li><ul><li>The cooldown of this ability has been reduced to 11/10/9/8/7, down from 12/11/10/9/8.</li></ul><li><B>Endless Delights (E)</B></li><ul><li>The cooldown of this ability has been reduced to 11/10/9/8/7, down from 12/11/10/9/8.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 29 (May 5th, 2014)</h4><ul><li><B>Captivate (Q)</B></li><ul><li>Fixed a bug where the tooltip of this ability was showing incorrect damage values.</li><li>Base damage now correctly display 35/55/75/95/115, fixed from displaying as 30/45/60/75/90.</li><li>Power ratio now correctly displays as 0.35, fixed from displaying as 0.25.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 26 (Feb 24, 2014)</h4><ul><li>Captivate (Q)</li><ul><li>The displayed range of this ability has been updated to 700, from previous value of 775.</li><li>The base damage of this ability has been reduced to 90/135/180/225/270, down from 105/165/225/285/345.</li><li>The Power ratio of this ability has been reduced to 0.75, down from 1.20.</li></ul><li>Flourish (W)</li><ul><li>The displayed range of this ability has been updated to 325, from previous value of 350.</li></ul><li>Endless Delights (E)</li><ul><li>The displayed range of this ability has been updated to 725, from previous value of 800.</li><li>The base damage of this ability per egg has been reduced to 55/90/125/160/195, down from 65/100/135/170/205.</li></ul><li>Finale (R)</li><ul><li>The displayed range of this ability has been updated to 805, from previous value of 900.</li><li>The Power ratio of this ability has been reduced to 0.7, down from 1.0.</li><li>The cooldown of this ability has been increased to 130/115/100, up from 120/105/90.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 22 (Jan 14, 2014)</h4><ul><li><B>Captivate (Q)</B></li><ul><li>Fixed a bug that was causing this ability to block pathing.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 20 (December 11, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>Captivate (Q)</B></li><ul><li>The Power ratio per hit on this ability has been reduced to 0.35, down from 0.4 (combined ratio now 1.05, down from 1.2)</li><li>The Flourished root duration on this ability has been increased to 1/1.25/1.5/1.75/2, up from 0.75/1/1.25/1.5/1.75</li><li>This ability now briefly reveals the target hit which now prevents a rare case where the tentacles collide with a target on the edge of the bush, slowing them but being unable to deal damage to them.</li><li>Fixed a bug that was causing this ability to go significantly further than max range when fired over certain walls.</li></ul><li><B>Endless Delights (E)</B></li><ul><li>The base damage per egg on this ability has been reduced to 65/100/135/170/205, down from 65/105/145/185/225.</li><li>The Power ratio per egg on this ability has been reduced to 0.7, down from .75.</li><li>Damage taken per egg for subsequent eggs hit past the first has been reduced to 25% damage, down from 35%.</li><li>The Flourished fear duration of this ability has been increased to 0.75/0.875/1/1.125/1.25, up from 0.5/0.6/0.7/0.8/0.9.</li><li>Fixed a bug where this ability could become interrupted if he was silenced immediately after casting this ability, even after the projectile was in flight.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 19 (November 27, 2013)</h4><ul><li>Fixed a bug that was causing the visual effects for Captivate (Q) to extend past the first target struck.</li><li>Fixed a bug that was causing the King of Masks to occasionally fire multiple instances of his abilities.</li><li>Fixed a bug that was causing the Endless Delights (E) to not deal area of effect damage.</li></ul>